### 8. Key Architecture Patterns

| Aspect | UseOnePortalSPA (New) | UseOnePortal (Legacy) |
|--------|----------------------|----------------------|
| **Target** | ASP.NET Core 8.0+ | Mixed scenarios |
| **SPA Dev Server** | Not configured | `UseReactDevelopmentServer("start")` |
| **Static Files** | Direct serving | `UseSpaStaticFiles()` |
| **Proxy Support** | Not built-in | Full proxy support |
| **Swagger** | Always available | Conditional (not with proxy) |
| **Fallback Routing** | `MapFallbackToFile("/index.html")` | Built into `UseSpa()` |

